\section*{Professional Summary}

Senior full stack engineer with 12+ years building production systems across web3, fintech, and enterprise applications. Backend specialist with deep expertise in distributed systems, microservices architecture, and high-performance computing. Proven track record designing and implementing complex full-stack applications from infrastructure to UX. Skilled in machine learning systems, from training neural operators and evolutionary algorithms to deploying adaptive trading systems. Strong architectural thinking combined with hands-on implementation across the entire stack—from smart contracts and backend APIs to responsive frontend UX and data pipelines.

