\section*{Selected Technical Projects}

\subsection*{Spinlock — Neural Operator Pre-Training Framework}
\textbf{GitHub:} \href{https://github.com/dgabriele/spinlock}{github.com/dgabriele/spinlock} | PyTorch, U-AFNO, Neural Operators, VQ-VAE

Pre-training framework for physics-native neural operators that discover emergent behaviors in high-dimensional dynamical systems. Implements curiosity-guided exploration using Sobol sampling, training U-AFNO meta-operators to generate fast surrogate models for diverse rollout dynamics. Compresses trajectories into hierarchical VQ-VAE tokens enabling semantic grounding across physics domains.

\subsection*{Nature — Genetic Programming Framework}
\textbf{GitHub:} \href{https://github.com/dgabriele/nature}{github.com/dgabriele/nature} | Python, Grammar Evolution

Open source framework that evolves Python instance methods via \texttt{@evolve} decorator. Multi-objective optimization over arbitrary datatypes (Pandas, NumPy, CuPy) outperforming DEAP. Built for generating adaptive trading rule ensembles.

\subsection*{Reactor — Procedural Generative Art Framework}
\textbf{GitHub:} \href{https://github.com/superginyuforce/reactor}{github.com/superginyuforce/reactor} | Node.js, TypeScript, Canvas API

Framework for procedural art generation with unified brush abstraction supporting parametric control over geometric primitives. Implements lazy evaluation proxy pattern for stroke dynamics with deterministic PRNG for reproducible variation. Produces high-resolution outputs (15000×15000px) for physical mockups and print-on-demand.

\subsection*{PampIt — Token Launchpad}
\textbf{GitHub:} \href{https://github.com/Gelotto/pampit}{github.com/Gelotto/pampit} | \textbf{Live:} \href{https://pampit.fun}{pampit.fun} | Next.js, Rust, CosmWasm

Production token launchpad across 6 Cosmos chains with zero backend infrastructure. Custom RPC batching client reducing distributed query latency 10x (4000ms $\rightarrow$ 400ms). Responsive UX with client-side pub/sub polling and pagination. All business logic in Rust smart contracts.

